      "content": "I get the environmental side, but it feels like a lot of people just dismiss the genetic hypothesis to avoid being controversial. Can you go into more detail about the actual arguments made by the researchers who suggest there might be a biological or hereditary component to these IQ gaps? Like, what's the logic they use to support that?",
